quran[123]{c,v,t}:
  11,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa, ko deftere nde aayeeje mun ñeñaa refti ɗe fensitaa immorde e oon Ñeeño kumpitiiɗo."
  11,2,"wota on ndw si winaa Alla.min dee komi jeertinoo jeertinoowo ummaade e makko, beltinoowo"
  11,3,"E nde imsintoɗon Joomi mon; refti tuubanon mo. O dakmita on dakamme labaaɗo haa e lajal innangal o jonna kala jom ɓural ɓural makko ngal. Si on nduŋtiima, haray min mi hulanii on lepte ñalaande mawnde."
  11,4,"Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde mon. Kaŋko ko O kattanɗo kala huunde."
  11,5,"Nganndee ɓeen ɗoon ɓe cowa ɓerɗe maɓɓe ɗen fii yo ɓe cuuɗo e makko. Nganndee fewndo ɓe cuddotortnoo comci maɓɓe ɗin, Homo anndi ko ɓe cuuɗata e ko ɓe peññinta. Pellet ko O gannduɗo ko woni e ɓerɗe ɗen."
  11,6,"Alaa e ruugayngel ka leydi si wanah ko Alla fawtii arsike maggel on, Homo anndi ñiiɓirde maggel e daakorde maggel; fof no e deftere ɓanngunde. Feeñnde"
  11,7,"Ko Kaŋko tagi kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin nder balɗe jeegoo, hari arsi makko kin no ka hoore ndiyam, fii yo o ndaarndo on ko hommbo e mo'on ɓurata moƴƴinnde gollal. Pellet si a wi'i: ""onon ko on ummintinteeɓe ɓaawo maayde"", maa heeferɓe ɓen mbi'u: ""ɗum wonaani si wonaa mbilewu peeñngu""."
  11,8,"Pellet si min neeɓaniiɓe lepte ɗen haa e dumunna limaaɗo, maa ɓe mbi'u: ""Ko tonngi ɗe?"" nganndee ñande nde arat e mabɓe, ɓe wonataa sureteeɓe e majje; jippoo e maɓɓe ɗuum ko laatinoo heɓe njalkita."
  11,9,"Si tawii min meeɗinii neɗɗaŋke on dokke immornde ka amen, refti min ɓoori nde e makko, kaŋko ko otaƴiido, yeddoowo."
  11,10,"Si tawii kadi minn meeɗinirii mo dokke ɓaawo lorra memɗo mo, maa o wi'oy : ""Satteende nden iwii e am"", kaŋko (ontuma) ko o beltiiɗo, ñaaƴoowo."
  11,11,"Si wonaa ɓeen muññii ɓe, ɓe ngolli golle moƴƴe. ɓeen ɗoon, no woodani ɓe haforanal e njoɓdi mawndi."
  11,12,"Yaamajo'o ko a accoowo yoga ko wahayinaa e maaɗa, ɓernde maa nden ɓiɗtora ɗum; fii heɓe mb'i: ""Ko haɗno ngalu jippinee e makko? maa Malaa'ika arda e makko?"" Anndu an ko a jertinoowo. Alla ko deenoowa kala huunde."
  11,13,"Kaa ɓe mbi'at : ""O fekindi nde?"" Maaku : ""ngaddee Corteeji( cimooje) sappo yeru mayre, pekindaaɗe, noddon kala mo haɗtanɗon gaanin Alla, si on laatike gooŋɗuɓe""."
  11,14,"Si ɓe njaabitaaki on, ngnndee won´de ko nde jippinira ko ganndal Alla, e won´de deweteeɗo alaa si wanaa Kaŋko. Hara onon ko on jebbiliiɓe?"
  11,15,"Kala on tawɗo ko nguurndam aduna e cuɗaari majjam faandii, min humnanay ɓe golle maɓɓe ɗen ton, hara kamɓe ɓe ustantaake ton."
  11,16,"Ko ɓeen ngoni ɓe alanah ɗum en ka laakara si wanaa Yiite. Ko ɓe ngolli ton kon firtii, ko meere woni koɓe ngollaynoo."
  11,17,"E ko oon laatiiɗo e ɓanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi makko, homo janngande mo seediiɗo immorde ka makko, e nde aditiinde mo [kaŋko Muhammadu], deftere Muusaa nden ardiinde e yurmeende [ɓuri moƴƴude diini ko alah hujja kon?]: Ɓen ɗon hino gooŋɗini nde; kala on jedduɗo nde e feddeeji ɗin, ko Yiite ngen woni fodoore makko. wota a laato e sikke fii mayre. Pellet ko nde goonga immornde ka Joomi maa; ko woni tun, ko ɓuri ɗuuɗude e yimɓe ɓen gooŋɗintaa."
  11,18,"Alaambo ɓuri tooñde ɓuri on pekandiido fenaa- nde e Alla? ɓeen ɗoon kolliroyte ka Joomi maɓɓe, (malaleykaaji) seediiɓe ɓen mbi'a: ""Ko ɓee ɗoo pennoo e Joomi maɓɓe"". Hey, kuddi Alla ndin wonii e tooñooɓe ɓeen."
  11,19,"Ɓeen falotooɓe ga e laawol Alla ngol, ɓe ɗaɓɓana ngol ooñorde, hara kadi ko ɓe yedduɓe laakara."
  11,20,"Ɓeen ɓe ngonaani laawotooɓe ka leydi, laatanaaki ɓe kadi weldiiɓe gaanin Alla, heɓe cowayanee lepte ɗeen. Ɓe laatanooki hattanɓe nangol, ɓe ngonaano kadi yi'ooɓe."
  11,21,"Ko ɓe ngoni sooyinɓe woŋkiiji mun ɗin. ɗuum ko ɓe pekintonoo majji gaay e maɓɓe."
  11,22,"Sikke alah, won`de ɓen ɗon ka laakara, ko kamɓe ɓuroyta sooyude."
  11,23,"Ɓeen gooŋɗinɓe, ɓe ngolli golle moƴƴe, ɓe njankinanii Joomi maɓɓe, ko ɓe ngoni yimɓe Aljanna ɓen, kamɓe ko ɓe duumotooɓe toon."
  11,24,"Misal peɗle ɗiɗi ɗe: ko wano bumɗo e pahɗuɗo, e ji'oowo e nanoowo. E ɓee ɗoo ɗiɗi fotat e misal? E on mbaajitotaako?"
  11,25,"Wollahi min nuliri Nuuhu e yimɓe makko ɓen: ""miin wonan´de on ko mi jertinoowo ɓannginɗo.(peeñɗo.)"
  11,26,"won´de wota on ndew si wanah Alla. min miɗo hulani on lepte ñalaande mu´usnde""."
  11,27,"Mbatu ɓeen yedduɓe e yimɓe makko ɓen mbi'i: min nji'aani ma si wonah ko a ɓanndiŋke sifa amen, men nj'aani kadi ɓen jokkuɓe ma si wo- naa jaasɓe amen faaɗuɓe feere, men nji'anaani on e amen ɓural. Worin miɗen cikki ko on fenooɓe""."
  11,28,"O maaki: ""eehey mon yo yimɓe am, kaalnee kam si tawii miɗo e ɓanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O weeɗii kam yurmeende (Annabaaku) immorde ka makko, ɗuum wumna e mooɗon, e min mbaaw- nay on nde hara ko on añɓe nde?"""
  11,29,"Eeheymon yo yimɓe am, mi laɓndaaki on jawdi e ɗuum. Njoɓdi am wonaani si wonah ka Alla. min mi wonaani raɗotooɗo ɓen gooŋɗinɓe, kamɓe ko ɓe hawroyooɓe Joomi maɓɓe. Ko woni tun, min mi yi'ii on yimɓe majjuɓe."
  11,30,"Eehey mon yimɓe am, ko hommbo walloytammi ka Alla si mi raɗike ɓe? E on mbaajitotaako?"
  11,31,"Mi wi'antah on miɗo mari ngaluujii Alla, mi annah kadi ko wirnii, mi wi'ataa won´de ko mi maleyko, mi wi'antaa ɓeen ɓe gite mon ɗen yawi, Alla okkoytaa-ɓe moƴƴere; ko Alla ɓuri anndude ko woni e woŋkiiji maɓɓe. miin ontuma [si mi waɗii ɗum], haray ko mi jeyaaɗo e tooñɓe ɓeen."
  11,32,"Ɓe mbi'i: ""Ko an yo Nuuhu, gooŋɗii a wenjidii e amen, a ɗuɗɗinii yeddondiral ngal e amen. Addan men ɗuum ko pod-ɗaa amen, si a laatike jeyaaɗo e goonguɓe ɓe""."
  11,33,"o maaki: ""nganndee ko Alla addanta on ɗe -si o muuyii- on ngonaani roŋkinooɓe."
  11,34,"Laaɓal-reedu am nafatah on, si mi faandike laaɓangol on, si tawii Alla no faandii bewnugol on (majjina). Ko Kaŋko woni Joomi mon, ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon."
  11,35,"Si ko woni, ɓe mbay : o fekindi-nde. Maaku: ""Si mi fekindi nde, haray bonnere am nden no fawii kam. min no ko mi daɗndiiɗo ko mbonnoton kon""."
  11,36,"Wahayinaa e Nuuhu won´de : ""Gooŋɗintah e yimɓe maa ɓen si wanaa ɓen gooŋɗinnooɓe. Wota a suno e ko ɓe ngollaynoo""."
  11,37,"Moƴƴin laana kan e ndeenka amen e yamiroore amen. Wota a yewtidoy e am fii ɓen tooñɓe, kamɓe ko ɓe yoolotooɓe."
  11,38,"Homo moƴƴina laana kan. Tuma kala nde dental hoorewal rewi ka o moƴƴinta ton, ɓe jalkita mo. o maaki: ""Si on jalkitii men, minen kadi min njalkitoyay on wano njalkitirton [men non]""."
  11,39,"Arma nde ngannduɗon ko hommbo lepte koynatɗe aroyat e muuɗum, lepte duumiiɗe njippoo e makko."
  11,40,"Haa si yamiroore amen nden aroyii, huɓɓinirɗe ɗen fati, min daali: ""Roondo e makka kala nooneeji ɗiɗi resindirayɗi e ɓeynguure maa nden -si wanaa ɓen konngol lepte ngol adii e mu'un- e ɓen gooŋɗinɓe"". Goosɗinaano won`dude e makko si wonah seeɗaaɓe."
  11,41,"O maaki: ""mbaɗɗee e makka e Innde Alla ka dogugol makka e daragol makko. Pellet Joomi am ko kaforoowo jurmotooɗo""."
  11,42,"Kan no dogida e maɓɓe e mollooɗe waaɗe wa pelle. Nuuhu noddi ɓiɗɗo makko on, hari on no serindi: ""eehey ma yo ɓinngel am, waɗɗida e amen, wata a won´du e yedduɓe ɓeen""."
  11,43,"O wi'i: ""Mi ƴawoyay e fello daɗndayngo kam ndiyam ɗam"". O maaki: ""Daɗoowo yamiroore Alla nden alaa hannde si wanah oon Mo O yurmini"". Molloonde nden heedi hakkunde maɓɓe, o laatodii e yoolaaɓe ɓen."
  11,44,"Wi'a: ""eeyma leydi, moɗ ndiyam maa ɗam! eeyma kadi yo kammu, jogito [sorombooji ndiyam ɗin]!"". Ndiyam ɗam ɓeeɓi, fiyaaku on ñaawaa, [laana] kan daroyii ka dow fello juudiiy, wi'aa: ""Halkaare woodanii ɓen yimɓe tooñɓe""."
  11,45,"Nuuhu noddi Joomi makko, o maaki: ""Joomi am, pellet ɓiɗɗo am on ko jeyaaɗo e ɓeynguure am, pellet fodoore maa nde ko goonga. Ko aan ɓuri nuunɗude ñaawoore ñaawooɓe""."
  11,46,"O daali: ""Ko an yo Nuuhu, pellet on jeyaaka e ɓeynguure maa, nden (toraare) ko gollal ngal moƴƴaa. Wata a toro kam ko a alanaa ɗum ganndal. min miɗo waajo maa fii wata a jeye e majjuɓe ɓeen""."
  11,47,"O maaki: ""Joomi am, mi moolorike ma nde mi lanndoto maa huunde nde mi alanah ɗum ganndal. Si wanaa A hafranam yurmin Ɗaa mi, mi jeyete e hayruɓe ɓen""(.pertuɓe)"
  11,48,"Wi'aa: ""Ko an yo Nuuhu, jippor kisiyee immorde ka amen, e moƴƴi dow maaɗaa e mofte won´duɓe e maaɗa. Mofte goo (no ton), aray min dakmita ɓe, refti memoya ɓe immorde e amen, lepte muusɗe""."
  11,49,"Ɗii ɗoo ko jeyaaɗi e kabaruuji birniiɗi, miɗen wahayina ɗe e maaɗa. A anndaano ɗe an, wanaa yimɓe maa ɓen, ko adii ɗum. Muñño, pellet battane moƴƴe ɗen woanii gooŋɗuɓe ɓen."
  11,50,"[minn Nulii] kadi faade e Aadinkooɓe ɓen, musiɗɗo maɓɓe on Huudi. O maaki : ""eeheymon yo yimɓe am, ndewee Alla, deweteeɗo alanah on ko woori mo. On ngonaani si wonaa fekindotooɓe""."
  11,51,"Eeheymon yimɓe am, mi laɓndaaki on e ɗuum njoɓdi. Njoɓdi am wonaani si wonaa ka on takɗo lam. En on haqqiltaa?"
  11,52,"Eheymon yimɓe am, imsinee ka Joomi mon, refti tuubanon mo o jippina e mooɗon toɓo jokkondirn-ngo, o ɓeyda on cemmbe e hoore cemmbe mon ɗen. Wota on nduŋto ngono ko on bonɓe."
  11,53,"Ɓe mbi'i: ""eheymaHuudu, kala ko addan-ɗaa men e ɓanngannduyee, minen men wonaani accooɓe deweteeɗi amen ɗin fii konngol maa ngol, minen min ngonaani gooŋɗinooɓe ma""."
  11,54,"Min mb'atah si wanaa yoga e deweteeɗi amen ɗin meminirii ma bone"". O maaki: ""Min miɗo seedina Alla -seeditee onon kadi- won´de min, ko mi daɗndiiɗo e ɗuum ko sirkoton,"
  11,55,"ga makko. Pewjanee kam on denndaangal, refti wata on padiree kam."
  11,56,"Min mi fawike e Alla, Joomi am e Joomi mon. Alaa e ruugayngel si wanaa ko O nannguɗo jubuuru maggel. Pellet, Joomi am no e laawol poocciingol."
  11,57,"Si on nduŋtii, gooŋɗii mi yottinanii kon ko mi nulidaa e mooɗon. Joomi am lomtinay yimɓe goo ɓe wonaa onon, on lorrirtaa mo hay e huunde. Pellet, Joomi am ko deeno kala huunde."
  11,58,"Nde yamiroore amen nden ari, min daɗndiri Huudi e ɓen goosɗinɓe won´duɓe e makko yurmeende amen. min daɗndi ɓe lepte tiiɗɗe."
  11,59,"Ɓeen ko Aadinkooɓe. e njedduno aayeeje Joomi amɓɓe ɗen, ɓe yeddi Nulaaɓe maɓɓe ɓen, ɓe jokki yamiroore kala dunndaranke sanndolɗinɗo."
  11,60,"Ɓe jokkindinaa ka aduna ɗoo, kuddi, e Ñande Darngal. ngnndee pellet, Aadinkooɓe ɓen njeddi Joomi maɓɓe. ngndee goɗɗal woodanii Aadi'en, yimɓe Huudi."
  11,61,"[Men Nulii] kadi e Samuuda'en, musiɗɗo maɓɓe Saalih, o maaki: ""eehey monyimɓe am, ndewee Alla. deweteeɗo alanaano on ko woori mo. Ko Kaŋko fuɗɗi on ka leydi, O wuurni on e mayri. Imsinanee mo, refti tuubon ka makko. Pellet Joomi am ko ɓaɗiiɗo, jaabotooɗo""."
  11,62,"Ɓe mbi'i: ""eeheyma Saalihu, gooŋɗii a woniino hakkunde amen jaakoraaɗo ado ɗum ɗoo. E a haɗay amen rewugol ko baabiraaɓe amen rewatno? Minen non, min ngonii e sikke e huunde nde noddataa amen e mun (sikke) jaaliiɗe""."
  11,63,"O maaki: ""eeheymon yimɓe! Kaalanee kam, si mi laatike e ɓanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O okkii kam immorde ka makko yurmeende, ko hommbo faabotoo mi ka Alla si mi yeddii mo? On ɓeydataa kam si wonaa hayrugol.perte"
  11,64,"Eeheymon yimɓe am, baa ɗoo ko ngelooba wonan´de on maande. Tertee mba, mba ñaama e leydi Alla. Wata on memir-mba bone, lepte ɓaɗtiiɗe keɓa on""."
  11,65,"Ɓe mborii-ba. o maaki: ""ndakmitee ka galleeji mon balɗe tati! Ɗuum ko fodoore nde fennetaake""."
  11,66,"Nde yamiroore Alla nden arunoo, min daɗndiri Saalihu e ɓen gooŋɗinɓe won´duɓe e makko, yur-meende immorde ka amen- e koyeera nden ñande Pellet Joomi maa, ko Kaŋko woni cemmbinɗo, pooluɗo."
  11,67,"Haacaango ngoon nanngi tooñuɓe ɓeen.Ɓe waɗtini ka galleeji maɓɓe jicciiɓe.(jusɓe)."
  11,68,"A sikkay ɓe ñiiɓaano ɗoon. Nganndee pellet Samuudu en njedduno Joomi maɓɓe, nganndee goɗɗal yurmee- nde (Alla) woodanii Samuuda'en!"
  11,69,"Gooŋɗii Nulaaɓe amen ɓeen nggaddanii Ibraahiima welo-welo, ɓe mbi'i: ""Kisal (e mon)"". O maaki: ""Kisal (e mon). Neeɓaani o ardi e ngaari juɗaandi."
  11,70,"Nde o yi'noo juuɗe maɓɓe ɗeen njottaaki ndi, o faytiɓe (o sikkitii), o soomi kulol e maɓɓe. Ɓe mbi'i: ""Wota a hul, ko min nulaaɓe e yimɓe Luuti ɓeen""."
  11,71,"Tawi cuddiiɗo makko on no darii, o jali, min mbeltiniri mo Ishaaqa, e ɓaawo Ishaaqa, Yaaquube."
  11,72,"[Debbo on] wi'i: ""Ee jalla am! emi jibinay e hoore ko mi nayeejo, e hino oo ɗoo gorko am ko nayeejo? Pellet ɗuum ɗoon ko huunde haawniinde!""."
  11,73,"Ɓe mbi'i: ""E a haawete fiyaaku Alla on? Yurmeende Alla e barkiiji makko ngonii e mon, yimɓe nduu suudu. Pellet ko O jettiniiɗo Tedduɗo""."
  11,74,"Nde kulol ngol iwnoo e Ibraahiima, welo-welo o ari e makko, homo yeddandira e amen fii yimɓe Luuti ɓeen."
  11,75,"Pellet, Ibraahiima ko muññiiɗo, keewɗo jankina-gol, tuuboowo."
  11,76,"Eheyma Ibraahiima, ɗuurno ga e ɗum; gooŋɗii yamiroore Joomi maa nden arii, e pellet, lepte aray e maɓɓe lepte ɗe nduuttetaake."
  11,77,"Nde nulaaɓe amen ɓen ngarnoo ka Luuti, o sunanii ɓe, o ɓiɗtori fonndo makko ngon fii maɓɓe, o maaki: ""ndee ɗoo ko ñalaande saɗtunde""."
  11,78,"Yimɓe makko ɓeen ngari e makko e yaccoo. Ado ɗum hari heɓe ngollaynoo bonɗi. O maaki: ""Eeheymon yimɓe am, ɓee ɗoo ko jiwɓe am: ko kamɓe ɓuri laaɓannde on. Kulee Alla, wata on kersinam e hoɓ- ɓe am. E gorko peewɗo alaa e mo'on?""."
  11,79,"Ɓe mi'i: ""Pellet haɗa anndi haaju alanah men e jiwɓe maa ɓeen, pellet haɗa anndi kadi ko men faalaako"" koy.."
  11,80,"O maaki: ""Sinno miɗo marunoo doole e mon! maa ɗuum mi fattinoo(moolo) e soɓɓundu sattundu(jookdu)!""."
  11,81,"[Hoɓɓe ɓen] mbi'i: ""eheymaLuutu, pellet ko men nulaaɓe Joomi maa. ɓe njottotaaka ema. Yaltinir ɓeynguure maa nden e taƴunnde jemma, wata gooto e mo'on yeƴƴito si wonaa cuddiiɗo maa on, ko fii heɓay mo ko heɓata ɓeya kon. Nganndon fodoore maɓɓe nden ka subaka. E subaka on laataaki ɓaɗiido?""."
  11,82,"Nde yamiroore amen nden arnoo, min waɗtiri dow [saare] nden ley mayre, min caaƴini e mayre kaaƴe iwruɗe loope juɗaaɗe dewondirɗe."
  11,83,"Maandinaaɗe ka Joomi maa. ɗe ngonaani goɗɗuɗe e tooñooɓe ɓeen."
  11,84,"[Min Nulii] kadi e Madyana'en, musiɗɗo maɓɓe on Shu'aybu, o maaki: ""eheymon yo yimɓe am, ndewee Alla; deweteeɗo alanaa on ko woori mo. Wota on ustu ɓetu ngun e manndake ɗen. min on miɗo yi'i on e moƴƴere. miin non miɗo hulani on lepte ñalaande fiiltiindede."
  11,85,"Eeheymon yo yimɓe am, timminee ɓetu ngun e manndake ɗen nuunɗal. Wata on ustan yimɓe ɓen coggu maɓɓe ngun, wata on njahru ka leydi bonnugol."
  11,86,"Ko keddiiɗe Alla ɗen ɓuri moƴƴannde on si on laatike gooŋɗinɓe. Mi wonaani deenoowo on""."
  11,87,"Ɓe mbi'i: ""eeheyma yo Shu'aybu! E ko juulde maa nden yamiru-maa nde men ngaccata rewugol ko baabiraa- ɓe amen ɓeen rewaynoo kon, maa nde men nggollata huuwata e jawle amen ɗen ko men njiɗi? Pellet an ko a muññiiɗo peewɗo""."
  11,88,"O maaki: ""eeheymon yo yimɓe am, kaalaneekam: si miɗo e ɓanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O arsikii lam immorde ka makko arsike moƴƴo?... mi faandaaki lunndaade on e kon haɗay-mi on e muuɗum. mi faandaaki si wonaa moƴƴingol fotde yeru am on. Kawral am wonaani si wonaa ka Alla. Ko e makko mi fawii, ko ka makko mi ruttotoo""."
  11,89,"Eehmon yimɓe am, wata ngañngu am defu on haa heɓa on sifa ko heɓnoo yimɓe Nuuhu maa yimɓe Huudi maa yimɓe Saalih. Yimɓe Luuti ɓen kan ngoɗɗaani on."
  11,90,"Imsinanee Joomi mon, refti tuubanon mo. Pelet Joomi am ko jurmotooɗo, Giɗo""."
  11,91,"Ɓe mbi'i: ""eeheyma Shu'aybu, men alah faamude ko ɗuuɗi e ɗuum ko mbi'ataa; minen miɗen ma nji'a hakku-nde amen lo'oɗo. Si wanaano gorol maa ngol, men piyirteno keeƴe. Aan a wonaani tedduɗo e amen""."
  11,92,"O maaki: ""E ko gorol am ngol ɓuri teddudo e mon diini Alla, on waɗtirii mo ɓaawo mon hawkaaɗo? Pellet Joomi am ko huɓindiiɗo(fiiltiido) ko ngollaton kon."
  11,93,"Eeheymon yimɓe am, ngollee e nokku mo'on. miin kadi ko mi golloowo. Arma nde nganndoton ko hombo lepte koynooje arat e mu'm e ko hommbo woni penoowo on. (Jooni non) padee! min kadi miɗo won´di e mon patndiiɗo."
  11,94,"Nde yamiroore amen nden arnoo, min daɗndiri Shu'aybu e ɓeen gooŋɗinɓe won´duɓe e makko yurmeende amen. Haacaango ngon nanngi ɓen tooñɓe, ɓe waɗtini ka cuuɗi maɓɓe jicciiɓe(.jusɓe)"
  11,95,"A wi'ay ɓe ñiiɓaano ɗon. ngandee woɗɗineede yurmeende wonanii Madayana wano Samuuda'en woɗɗiniranoo."
  11,96,"Gooŋɗii Men Nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje amen ɗeen e hujja ɓannguɗo."
  11,97,"Ha e Fir'awna e mbatu mun. ɓe njokkii yamiroore Fir'awna nden, yamiroore Fir'awna non wanaa feewnde."
  11,98,"O ardoyto yimɓe makko ɓeen ñande darngal, o jolna ɓe ka Yiite. (Nge)bonii jolirde jolaande."
  11,99,"Ɓe njokkinaama kuddi e oo (aduna), e ñande Darngal. Bonii ballal ngal ɓe njokkindiranaa."
  11,100,"Ɗuum ko jeyaaɗum e kumpite ce'e, miɗen fillano maa ɗuum: no e majje ñiiɓɗe e coñaaɗe."
  11,101,"Min tooñaani ɓe. Ko woni, ko kamɓe tooñi ko'e maɓɓe. deweteeɗi maɓɓe ɗiin ɗiɓe ndwatnoo gah ɗin duncanaali ɓe hay e huunde, tuma nde yamiroore Joomi maa nden arnoo; ɗi ɓeydaani ɓe si wonaa hayrude."
  11,102,"Ko wano nii nanngal Joomi maa ngal, si tawii o nanngii ce'e ɗen hara ko ɗe tooñɗe. Pellet nanngal makko ngal ko muusngal caɗtungal."
  11,103,"Pellet tasakuyee wonii e ɗuum ɗoo wonan´de on kulɗo lepte laakara. nden ko ñalaande yimɓe en mooɓoyte e mun, nde kadi ko ñalaande seedoyteende."
  11,104,"Min neeɓtinataa nde si wanah haa e lajal limangal."
  11,105,"Ñalnde ngal arata, woŋkii (woo) wowlatah si wanaa e duŋayee makko. Hino e maɓɓe malkisaaɗo e malaaɗo."
  11,106,"Si ko malkisaaɓe ɓen, ko ka Yiite; hino woodani ɓe ndeer ton ottaango e hiikaango."
  11,107,"Ko ɓe luttinteeɓe ndeer magge fotde kammuuli ɗiin e leydi ndin no duumii, si wonah si Joomii maa muuyii; pellet Joomi maa ko baɗoowo kala ko O faandii."
  11,108,"Si tawii non ko malaaɓe ɓen, ko ka ndeer Aljanna woni ko duumintee e mun fotde kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin no duumii, si wanaa si Joomi maa muuyii. (Ɗum) ko dokkal ngal taƴondirtaa."
  11,109,"Wota a won e sikke e huunde ko ɓee ndewata. ɓe rewiraani si wanaa no baabiraaɓe maɓɓe ndewiray- noo ko adii. minen non, min hunniranay ɓe geɗal maɓɓe ngal ko aldah e ustugol."
  11,110,"Gooŋɗii min ngkkii Muusaa Deftere nden, luutondi- raa e mayre. Si wanaano konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, ñaaweteno hakkunde maɓɓe. Kamɓe kan heɓe e sikke sikkitiiɗo e e mayre."
  11,111,"Wonaani kala maɓɓe si wonaa Joomi maa hunna- nay ɓe (njoɓdi) kuuɗe maɓɓe. Pellet ko O kumpitiiɗo ko ɓe ngollata kon."
  11,112,"Ñiiɓir [e pocciingol ngol] wano njamiraɗaa non, e tuubuɓe won´duɓe e maaɗa. wota on mbew. Pellet ko O deenɗo ko ngolloton kon."
  11,113,"Wata on ooñor e tooñuɓe ɓen sakko Yiite ngen mema on. Alanah on gah ni Alla yiɗɓe. refti on mballoytaake."
  11,114,"Ñiiɓnu juulde nde ka seraaji ɗiɗi ñalawma e saa'iiji jemma. Pellet moƴƴi ɗin hino momta bonɗi ɗin. Ɗuum ko waaju wonan´de ɓeen waajitotooɓe."
  11,115,"Muñño. pellet Alla yeebataa njoɓdi moƴƴinooɓe ɓeen."
  11,116,"Ko haɗnoo wona e gire adinooɓe on ɓen, joomiraa- ɓe kedde, ɓe no haɗa e bonnugol ka leydi! si seeɗaaɓe e ɓen ɓe min ndaɗndunoo e maɓɓe. Tooñuɓe ɓen nokki e ko ɓe neeminaa e mun kon, ɓe laatii bonɓe."
  11,117,"Joomi maa siforaani kalkiroowo ce'e e hoore tooñe tawa yimɓe maɓɓe ko moƴƴinooɓe."
  11,118,"Sinno Joomi maa muuyiino, O waɗatno yimɓe ɓen moftal gootal. ɓe ceerataa ko ɓe luutondirooɓe."
  11,119,"si wanaa ɓeen ɓe Joomi maa yurmaa. Ko sabu ɗuum O tagiri ɓe. Konngol Joomi maa ngol jojjii won´de: ""Pellet, Mi hebbiniray Jahannama jinna e yimɓe, ɓe denndaangal""."
  11,120,"Kala e mu'un, miɗen fillano maa kabaruuji Nulaaɓe, ko min tabintinra ɗuum ɓernnde maa ngon. Aranii ma e ngol (cortewol) goonga e waaju e janntoore wonan´de gooŋɗinɓe ɓen."
  11,121,"Maakan ɓeen ɓe gooŋɗinah: ""NGollee e nokku mo'on. minen kadi, ko min gollooɓe."
  11,122,"Padee kadi. minen ko men fatndiiɓe""."
  11,123,"Ko Alla heeranii birniiɗi kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin, ko ka makko fiyaaku no fow ruttetee. Awa rewu Mo, fawo-ɗaa e makko. Joomi maa wonaani belsindiiɗo e ɗuum ko ngolloton."
